reviewText: Yea, its perverted, crazy, and over the top but if your into ecchi mixed with animation that is reminiscent of 1970s style japanese animation, you will love this one.

Should you hear your 10-13 year old daughter and her girlfriends snickering and giggling behind a locked door on a boring night,they may be having a bit of amusement with this tripe. If your son finds it of interest,expect an anouncement of some concern for both his sexual choice and lack of intellectual developement prospects as this waste of time and money is boring,childish,disjointed and obsessed with Prince Enma's penis,his "Moby Dick",each episode somehow manages to work something concerning it into the storyline.
The advertised "nude" princess may be naked but you can only presume such as something is always in the way to confirm it.
Lame,boring,waste of time and over priced, I have to find some other damn fool to sell this to or just toss it in the box of likewise crap and let my hiers worry about.
